[Name] Pidgin-FacebookChat
[Summary] Facebook chat plugin for Pidgin
[Description] This is a Facebook chat plugin for Pidgin and libpurple
messengers. It connects to the new Facebook Chat IM service without
the need for an API key. 
Currently the plugin can log into the Facebook servers, grab the buddy
list, send/receive messages, add/remove friends, receive
notifications, search for Facebook friends and set your Facebook status.
